Here is a summary of the service <%=v.name%>:
Type: <%=v.type%>.
Name:  <%= v.name %>.
Details:  <%= v.details %>.
<% v.puppets.each do |p| %>
    Puppet "<%=p%>.pp" has been used to create this service.
<% end %>
<% end %>

==Vulnerabilities==
